snippet: The quake was powerful, but the mountainous region where it occurred is sparsely populated.
abstract: Mountainous part of Xinjiang region in western China is hit by powerful earthquake, destroying dozens of homes although there are no initial reports of deaths in thinly populated area.
lead_paragraph: The quake was powerful, but the mountainous region where it occurred is sparsely populated.

headline.main: Earthquake Strikes Remote Area of China
